<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Intelligence (INT) is the stat affecting failure rate for this skill. <h3 id="head-999ea98a9f3cd197db5ccfbe49cb700d8e21f554">Mana Spells</h3>
The mana school contains spells where the raw force of magic is used to create the final spell effect. <p>
There are four spells available for the mana school: 
</p>

    <ol type="1">

    <li>
<p>
<strong>Manathrust</strong> (school level 1) Conjures up mana into a powerful bolt. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 The damage is irresistible and will increase with spell level. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Remove Curses</strong> (school level 10) Removes curses from worn objects. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 At spell level 20 switches to *remove curses*. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Elemental Shield</strong> (school level 20) Provide resistance to the four basic elements. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 Duration increases with spell level. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Disruption Shield</strong> (school level 45) Uses mana instead of hitpoints to take damage. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 At spell level 5 switches to Globe of Invulnerability. 
</p>
</li>
                <li>
<p>
 The spell breaks as soon as a melee, shooting, throwing or magical skill action is attempted, and lasts only a short time. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>    </ol>


<h4 id="head-3ce56f72b52e5daf6171d3ddcb0f5a654e4629c9">Combined Spells</h4>
<p>
There is one combined school spell available for the Mana school: 
</p>

    <ol type="1">

    <li>
<p>
<strong>Drain</strong> (dual school: Mana/Udun level 1) Drains the mana contained in wands, staves and rods to increase yours. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 Your Mana and <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fUdun"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Udun</a> skills must have reached a combined average level of 1 in order to cast this spell. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>    </ol>


<h4 id="head-906abc02ff3d872f162af0a481dce9a5c5462baa">God given ability</h4>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fIntroduction_20to_20the_20Gods_20of_20ToME#head-830bd605821ee79b05019df0d67000cd17c87ff6"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Eru Iluvatar</a> at 1/2 prayer level. 
</p>
</li>
</ul>

